{"tid":1155744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長實據報出售上海大型地產項目股權 估值200億人幣","createTime":"2019-05-15T06:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T05:11:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"455a040772dd7dc373d1719dbb15e2d2d983e9b1","tid":1155744,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"長實據報出售上海大型地產項目股權 估值200億人幣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2349654/%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%20%20%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC200%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2349654%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E9%25A0%2585%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%2582%25A1%25E6%25AC%258A%2520%2520%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2580%25BC200%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B9%25A3&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=aa678cc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2349654/%E9%95%B7%E5%AF%A6%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E9%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E8%82%A1%E6%AC%8A%20%20%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC200%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3</a><br />\n<br />\n長實(01113)據報考慮出售上海一個大型開發項目權益。彭博引述消息人士報道，擬出售的項貝名為高&middot;尚領域，位於上海西北部普陀區，項目總建築面積逾110萬平方米。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，長實集團持有該項目60%權益，整個項目的估值可能約為200億元人民幣（約29億美元）。長實網站指出，該項目是目前上海最大規模城市綜合發展項目之一，結集商場、辦公室、住宅、服務式住宅及酒店物業。"},{"pid":"4e9b47085d76a6c9e9af872f368b6abc5ca48d7f","tid":1155744,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"作反了"},{"pid":"d1a1b404ccb829fb735cfe42cd44fe136533f529","tid":1155744,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"是但啦屌 關我閪事"},